data.description:
Pride in ownership shows in this home located on a corner lot in Sendera Ranch with open space across the street. Gorgeous wood-look tile floors welcome you as you enter the home creating seamless elegance with this thoughtfully designed open floor plan home. Bathed in natural light, the spacious living area seamlessly flows into the kitchen and two living areas, creating a harmonious and inviting atmosphere with flexible spaces. The open layout provides endless possibilities for furniture arrangement, allowing you to personalize the space to suit your lifestyle. The updated fireplace accent wall creates a focal point perfect for your holiday and seasonal decor.  From intimate dinners to lively gatherings, this home is an entertainer's dream.

The oversized backyard where you can create your own oasis showcasing an extended patio! Sendera Ranch is a sought-after community and part of the Northwest Independent School District.
